            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1685530013132-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1685530013132-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>five-spice roasted duck</strong> with the <strong>sesame roasted veg </strong>and <strong>cooked rice</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>plum sauce </strong>over the duck</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
